<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>A <db:link xlink:href="qt3dinput-qmousedevice.xml">QMouseDevice</db:link> delegates mouse events from physical mouse device to <db:link xlink:href="qt3dinput-qmousehandler.xml">QMouseHandler</db:link> objects. The sensitivity of the mouse can be controlled with the <db:link xlink:href="qt3dinput-qmousedevice.xml#sensitivity-prop">QMouseDevice::sensitivity</db:link> property, which specifies the rate in which the logical mouse coordinates change in response to physical movement of the mouse.</db:para>
